row.Title: Get a 25% Bonus When You Convert Marriott Points to United Miles The Points Guy
row.Selection: Through March 31, 2016, you can earn a 25% bonus when you transfer Marriott Rewards points to United MileagePlus — this is on top of the regular 20% bonus you’ll receive when converting Marriott points into United miles, as part of the duo’s RewardsPlus partnership. This bonus is especially valuable when paired with Marriott’s Hotel +...
